trans-unit.source: Represents a line used to group items of a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip"></xref> or the drop-down items of a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.MenuStrip"></xref> or <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ContextMenuStrip"></xref> or other <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripDropDown"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Representa uma linha usada para agrupar itens de um <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip"> </xref> ou os itens de lista suspensa de um <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.MenuStrip"> </xref> ou <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ContextMenuStrip"> </xref> ou outros <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripDropDown"> </xref> controle.

trans-unit.source: Use a ToolStripSeparator to group related items on a menu or <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip>.
trans-unit.target: Use um ToolStripSeparator para agrupar itens relacionados em um menu ou <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip>

trans-unit.source: The ToolStripSeparator is automatically spaced and oriented horizontally or vertically to accord with its container.
trans-unit.target: O ToolStripSeparator é automaticamente espaçado e orientada horizontal ou verticalmente de acordo com seu contêiner.

trans-unit.source: You can add a ToolStripSeparator at design time by choosing it from a drop-down list.
trans-unit.target: Você pode adicionar um ToolStripSeparator em tempo de design selecionando-a em uma lista suspensa.

trans-unit.source: However, you can also automatically create a ToolStripSeparator by typing a hyphen (-) in either the designer template node or in the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripItemCollection.Add%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: No entanto, você pode criar automaticamente um ToolStripSeparator digitando um hífen (-) no nó designer de modelo ou no <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripItemCollection.Add%2A>método.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripItemCollection.Add%2A>
